    "div" : "<div xml:lang=\"fr-FR\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" lang=\"fr-FR\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Narratif généré : EnsembleValeurs jdv-hl7-v3-CoverageRoleType-cisis</b></p><a name=\"jdv-hl7-v3-CoverageRoleType-cisis\"> </a><a name=\"hcjdv-hl7-v3-CoverageRoleType-cisis\"> </a><div style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: #d9e0e7; padding: 6px; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid #8da1b4; border-radius: 5px; line-height: 60%\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">version : 7; Dernière mise à jour : 2026-02-23 14:57:30+0100; Langue : fr-FR</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">Profil: <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/shareablevalueset.html\">Shareable ValueSetversion : null4.0.1)</a></p></div><ul><li>Include ce(s) code(s) tel qu'il(s) est (sont) défini(s) dans <a href=\"CodeSystem-v3-RoleCode.html\"><code>http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v3-RoleCode</code></a><span title=\"La version est explicitement indiquée comme étant 3.0.0\"> version &#x1F4CD;3.0.0</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Affichage</b></td><td><b>Définition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-v3-RoleCode.html#v3-RoleCode-FAMDEP\">FAMDEP</a></td><td>Couverture familiale</td><td>The player of the role is dependent of the scoping entity.</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-v3-RoleCode.html#v3-RoleCode-STUD\">STUD</a></td><td>Couverture étudiante</td><td>Covered party to an insurance policy has coverage through full-time or part-time attendance at a recognized educational institution as defined by a particular insurance policy.</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-v3-RoleCode.html#v3-RoleCode-SELF\">SELF</a></td><td>Couverture personnelle</td><td>Covered party is the policy holder. Also known as the subscriber.</td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"
